milestones.description: Viswanath has become the top scorer for IND in ODIs with 276 runs, going past Gavaskar's 254
Viswanath has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (13) for IND, going past Srinivas Venkataraghavan
Syed Kirmani and Sandeep Patil's 92-run partnership is the highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 77 between Alan Knott and Tony Greig
